  "detailed_description": "ToledoVR is a action/strategy game for the HTC Vive. <br><br>Play as a god from the top and fight as a hero on the ground. <br><br>Playable both in VR and on the PC simultaneously (local multiplayer).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 1:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/557460/extras/8aaf802b70575bb2bc81260911665720.avif?t=1518032829\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gametype: MOBA (Use waves of units to destroy towers and finally the enemy)<br></li><li>Gamemodes: Singleplayer (vs AI), local multiplayer (1vs1)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 2:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/557460/extras/9306e9aa62b789f4d99886829f32da1d.avif?t=1518032829\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gametype: RTS (Erect buildings and command units in real time)<br></li><li>Gamemodes: Singleplayer (vs AI), local multiplayer (1vs1), local coop (survival mode)</li></ul>",
